# ResourceManagerSystem

## Purpose
One-shot initialization system. On the first frame, loads all textures, fonts, shaders, UI
layouts, sound clips, JSON assets, and 3D models from `Assets/Engine/ResourcesManifest.json` and
`Assets/App/ResourcesManifest.json`, then creates ResourceMapSingletonComponent containing the fully
populated asset maps. No-op on all subsequent frames (presence check guards early exit).

## Input Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| ResourceMapSingletonComponent | read | Presence-check only; if present, system exits immediately |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| ResourceMapSingletonComponent | add (deferred) | Created once; holds texture, shader, font, UI layout, sound clip, parsed JSON asset, and 3D model maps keyed by UUID |
